TokenWatch is an independent, unofficial tool. It is not affiliated with,
endorsed by, or sponsored by Anthropic or OpenAI. "Claude", "Claude Code",
"Codex", and related marks belong to their respective owners.

This software reads usage data from the user's own local Claude Code / Codex
configuration and queries each provider's web endpoints using the user's own
authenticated session. Those endpoints are undocumented and may change at any
time.
